==與其他聖典的關係==
德國學者Hinuber 認為自說經是屬於早期九分教的部份，因此自說經雖是歸入晚期成書的小部，但其內容卻是貼近佛世時代的<ref name="Hinüber2000">{{Cite book|author=Oskar von Hinüber|title=''A Handbook of Pāli Literature''|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8jPYUCy-GxQC&pg=PA46|year=2000|publisher=Walter de Gruyter|isbn=978-3-11-016738-2|pages=7(§10),46(§91)|quote=The Udāna ... belongs to those old texts mentioned already as one of the navaṅga.... [I]t does not seem to be impossible that there once was an Ud having only verses such as those in the Udānavarga....|access-date=2018-07-03|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809010237/https://books.google.com/books?id=8jPYUCy-GxQC&pg=PA46|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dsalsrv02.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/philologic/getobject.pl?c.1:1:2826.pali |title=Rhys Davids & Stede (1921–1925), p. 348, entry for "Nava" |access-date=2018-07-03 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809010247/http://dsalsrv02.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/philologic/getobject.pl?c.1:1:2826.pali |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他亦認為自說經部份觀點亦可在[[奧義書|奧義書]]及[[耆那教|耆那教]]經典中見到。

